        <h1 class="proj-title">Café Nova:<br>A Margin Collapse</h1>
        <p class="proj-sub">A 30-minute management-consulting case, worked end to end. A coffee chain grows 15% and its margin falls from 25% to 7%. The board wants an explanation. Here's how I'd structure it, and where I'd commit.</p>
        <div class="stack-row">
